title: #498 - Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt
description:
Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio talking about why Joey is sick of fear; and how he has learned to combat it in his life.  Joey also speaks about a book he was given, "The Art of War for Writers"  by James Scott Bell.
